* The Hyakki Yagyō (a procession of Yōkai and ghosts, similar to Hecate&#x27;s)
* Melinoë
* The Nightmarchers (a procession of ghosts, similar to Hecate&#x27;s)
* The Unseelie Court (a procession of ghosts, similar to Hecate&#x27;s)
* The Wild Hunt (a procession of ghosts, similar to Hecate&#x27;s)

